## <a id='releases'></a> Releases

### <a id='2-9-alpha'></a> 2.9.0 Alpha 1

* **[Feature]** Operators can view and update internal authentication settings by using the Ops Manager `/api/v0/settings/authentication` API endpoint or by accessing the **Settings** pane of the Ops Manager UI.
* **[Feature]** Operators can update the Ops Manager decryption passphrase by using the Ops Manager `/api/v0/settings/decryption-passphrase` API endpoint.
* **[Feature]** Operators can view and update proxy settings in Ops Manager by using the Ops Manager `/api/v0/settings/proxy_settings` API endpoint.
* **[Feature]** When in Advanced Mode, operators can update additional fields related to blobstore location, Luna HSM, GCS blobstore and S3 blobstore settings in the **Director Config** screen after deploying the BOSH Director. Previously the fields were frozen after deployment.
* **[Feature]** Ops Manager supports domain-style URLs as the default for configuring AWS S3 compatible blobstores.
* **[Feature]** Ops Manager API documentation now follows the OpenAPI Specification (OAS). This update provides operators with a machine-parsable version of the Ops Manager API docs and improves general formatting.
* **[UI Improvement]** When in Advanced Mode, operators see a special banner in the Ops Manager UI.

